## KEY INDUSTRY DEVELOPMENTS
* March 2024: Laitram Machinery acquired Martak's shrimp peeling business line in 2024.
* February 2024: An Indian online seafood-selling company “Captain Fresh” acquired U.S.-based seafood importer “CenSea Inc.”
* June 2022: “Ocean 14 Capital Fund” entered into a definitive agreement with USD 12 million to purchase a majority stake in “SyAqua”.
* March 2020: Sykes Seafood, a Liverpool-based seafood provider, acquired European shrimp processor Klaas Puul.
* February 2019: Cooke aquaculture, a Scottish company, acquired “Seajoy” a decapod crustaceans producer based in Honduras.

